{"tid":1100710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"慎入！！！童喝夜奶滿口爛牙！醫縫18血洞嚇傻","createTime":"2019-04-10T14:43:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-10T16:45:17.000Z","uid":215574,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"213e4da51cee078b458c61279f090a8cde97bd27","tid":1100710,"uid":215574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T14:43:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hoC05nhBJMGwNTBqm72pPOzcaMwM-ICNvaXphb04iblhyLCJuZix_WSEYPglwf3cyY393Di5FK10oKCc6Ni1_/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hoC05nhBJMGwNTBqm72pPOzcaMwM-ICNvaXphb04iblhyLCJuZix_WSEYPglwf3cyY393Di5FK10oKCc6Ni1_%2Fw644&h=b7e8717f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n<br />\n泰國一名醫師透露，日前幫4歲孩童看診時，發現對方整口牙齒幾乎全爛光，不得已只好拔除18顆乳牙，事後詢問家長才得知，原來這名孩童平時有喝「夜奶」的習慣，喝完也沒有進行潔牙步驟，經常直接抱著奶瓶入睡，久而久之，牙齒就被蛀光光了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hntL0GB9vMVtxSRuRk29ODEsfMjRCJSJYFX9gWDInb28OKSNZGil-bl1MZ2MLeHYFH3p2OVJNKmpULSYNSih-/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hntL0GB9vMVtxSRuRk29ODEsfMjRCJSJYFX9gWDInb28OKSNZGil-bl1MZ2MLeHYFH3p2OVJNKmpULSYNSih-%2Fw644&h=b1bfa51a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲拔牙過程出動4名醫護人員。（圖／翻攝自中國報）<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，負責診治的牙醫師指出，這名孩童前來看診時滿口爛牙，最後只能拔除18顆乳牙，拔牙過程甚至出動了4名醫護人員。而家長事後也坦承，平時只要孩子半夜哭鬧不止，他們就會餵奶進行安撫，喝完之後也常常讓孩子直接抱著奶瓶入睡，沒有再多做潔牙步驟。<br />\n<img src=\"https://obs.line-scdn.net/0hoC05nhBJMGwNTBqm72pPOzcaMwM-ICNvaXphb04iblhyLCJuZix_WSEYPglwf3cyY393Di5FK10oKCc6Ni1_/w644\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fobs.line-scdn.net%2F0hoC05nhBJMGwNTBqm72pPOzcaMwM-ICNvaXphb04iblhyLCJuZix_WSEYPglwf3cyY393Di5FK10oKCc6Ni1_%2Fw644&h=b7e8717f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲4歲童牙齒幾乎被拔光，縫了18個血洞。（圖／翻攝自中國報）<br />\n<br />\n對此，牙醫師就提醒，許多小孩睡前都有喝夜奶、吃東西的習慣，如果事後沒做好口腔清潔，讓食物滯留嘴巴過久孳生細菌，很容易導致早發性齲齒，所以飯後、睡前的潔牙步驟千萬不可少，才能讓降低蛀牙的發生率。（編輯：鄭餘蓉）<br />\n<a href=\"https://today.line.me/tw/pc/article/%E7%AB%A5%E5%96%9D%E5%A4%9C%E5%A5%B6%E6%BB%BF%E5%8F%A3%E7%88%9B%E7%89%99+%E9%86%AB%E7%B8%AB18%E8%A1%80%E6%B4%9E%E5%9A%87%E5%82%BB-YeVQya\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftoday.line.me%2Ftw%2Fpc%2Farticle%2F%25E7%25AB%25A5%25E5%2596%259D%25E5%25A4%259C%25E5%25A5%25B6%25E6%25BB%25BF%25E5%258F%25A3%25E7%2588%259B%25E7%2589%2599%2B%25E9%2586%25AB%25E7%25B8%25AB18%25E8%25A1%2580%25E6%25B4%259E%25E5%259A%2587%25E5%2582%25BB-YeVQya&d=CmE1Ecd1w6veVISTpL%2FBTpgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=6f2b6fb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://today.line.me/tw/pc/article/%E7%AB%A5%E5%96%9D%E5%A4%9C%E5%A5%B6%E6%BB%BF%E5%8F%A3%E7%88%9B%E7%89%99+%E9%86%AB%E7%B8%AB18%E8%A1%80%E6%B4%9E%E5%9A%87%E5%82%BB-YeVQya</a>"},{"pid":"0b2e29372869a44d3be95f6e9f048d5f57a9858c","tid":1100710,"uid":80724,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:22:44.000Z","msg":"呢啲永遠有高清大圖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"611079f05b8227dd2daa809c96b2a3078e9579d0","tid":1100710,"uid":182499,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"點解得人類咁弱要刷牙 動物會唔會蛀牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9668b92c5da85fc8fcb383b41b3db565387d8c5d","tid":1100710,"uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:34:59.000Z","msg":"第時會生返？"},{"pid":"cb8238be27c571d4b602777a4db74f1e9aa3312d","tid":1100710,"uid":228963,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:35:50.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1f609a242420783dc3d2ff95cd35a25a508f845b","tid":1100710,"uid":146435,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"611079f05b8227dd2daa809c96b2a3078e9579d0","tid":1100710,"uid":182499,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:30:42.000Z","msg":"點解得人類咁弱要刷牙 動物會唔會蛀牙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-10T15:36:53.000Z","msg":"佢係食得甜野先會蛀牙姐<br />\n利申：：十幾年未刷過牙 未蛀過牙"},{"pid":"7f9ee4611a3ba057372a317717d2a47d5